         <abstract id="aspace_78b537f83c27fda6cf44de52853a2a6e">The Bertita Harding writings consists of drafts and setting copies, typescript and typescript carbon, corrected, for Harding's biographical and historical works from the 1930s and 1950s.</abstract>
